question: Which counties border with Nottinghamshire?
sparql: SELECT ?county WHERE { yago:Nottinghamshire geo:hasGeometry ?geomLC . ?geomLC geo:asWKT ?lcWKT . ?county rdf:type y2geoo:OS_County ; geo:hasGeometry ?geomC . ?geomC geo:asWKT ?cWKT FILTER geof:sfTouches(?lcWKT, ?cWKT) }

question: What is the largest island that belongs to the UK?
sparql: SELECT ?island WHERE { yago:United_Kingdom geo:hasGeometry ?ukGeo . ?ukGeo geo:asWKT ?ukWKT . ?island rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_island ; geo:hasGeometry ?iGeo . ?iGeo geo:asWKT ?iWKT FILTER geof:sfWithin(?iWKT, ?ukWKT) } ORDER BY DESC(strdf:area(?iWKT)) LIMIT 1

question: Which is the largest region of Greece?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?region (strdf:area(?rWKT) AS ?totalArea) WHERE { ?region rdf:type y2geoo:GAG_Region ; geo:hasGeometry ?geomR . ?geomR geo:asWKT ?rWKT } ORDER BY DESC(?totalArea) LIMIT 1

question: Which streams cross forests located south of Oxford?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?stream WHERE { yago:Oxford geo:hasGeometry ?geomLC . ?geomLC geo:asWKT ?lcnWKT . ?stream rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_stream ; geo:hasGeometry ?geomP . ?geomP geo:asWKT ?lWKT_P . ?forest rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_forest ; geo:hasGeometry ?geomF . ?geomF geo:asWKT ?lWKT_F FILTER ( strdf:below(?lWKT_F, ?lcnWKT) && strdf:crosses(?lWKT_P, ?lWKT_F) ) }

question: Is county Cavan east of county Mayo?

question: Which forests are entirely within a barony and intersect with townlands?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?l WHERE { ?m rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_Barony ; geo:hasGeometry ?mg . ?mg geo:asWKT ?mw . ?l rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_forest ; geo:hasGeometry ?lg . ?lg geo:asWKT ?lw . ?townland rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_Townland ; geo:hasGeometry ?lg1 . ?lg1 geo:asWKT ?lw1 FILTER geof:sfWithin(?lw, ?mw) FILTER geof:sfIntersects(?lw, ?lw1) }

question: How many counties are there in California?
sparql: SELECT (COUNT(?county) AS ?numCounties) WHERE { yago:California geo:hasGeometry ?geom . ?geom geo:asWKT ?mWKT . ?county y2geoo:hasGADM_Description "County" ; geo:hasGeometry ?geomC . ?geomC geo:asWKT ?cWKT FILTER geof:sfContains(?mWKT, ?cWKT) }

question: Which is the smallest beach in the Peloponnese prefecture?
sparql: SELECT ?forest (strdf:area(?forestWKT) AS ?forestArea) WHERE { y2geor:gadmentity_Peloponnese_GRC.7.2_1 geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?pWKT . ?forest rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_beach ; geo:hasGeometry ?o3 . ?o3 geo:asWKT ?forestWKT FILTER geof:sfWithin(?forestWKT, ?pWKT) } ORDER BY ASC(?forestArea) LIMIT 1

question: How many lakes are north of forests in Cambridgeshire?
sparql: SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?park) AS ?parks) WHERE { yago:Cambridge geo:hasGeometry ?oGeo . ?oGeo geo:asWKT ?oWKT . ?park rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?parkGeometry . ?parkGeometry geo:asWKT ?parkWKT . ?stream rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_forest ; geo:hasGeometry ?streamGeometry . ?streamGeometry geo:asWKT ?streamWKT FILTER ( ( geof:sfContains(?oWKT, ?parkWKT) && geof:sfContains(?oWKT, ?streamWKT) ) && strdf:above(?parkWKT, ?streamWKT) ) }

question: Which localities are adjacent to lakes?

question: Are there any streams that cross villages in Central Greece?

question: Which is the least populated regional unit that belongs to the South Aegean administrative region and intersects with beaches?

question: Which municipalities in Greece have a population of less than 30000?

question: How many counties of Texas are larger than Austin?

sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?park (strdf:area(?pWKT) AS ?totalArea) WHERE { ?park rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_park ; geo:hasGeometry ?pGeom . ?pGeom geo:asWKT ?pWKT . yago:geoentity_Dimos_Athens_8133876 geo:hasGeometry ?lcGeom . ?lcGeom geo:asWKT ?lcWKT FILTER geof:sfWithin(?pWKT, ?lcWKT) } ORDER BY DESC(?totalArea) LIMIT 1

question: How many cities are north of streams, in Wales?
sparql: SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?county) AS ?cities) WHERE { yago:Wales geo:hasGeometry ?oGeo . ?oGeo geo:asWKT ?oWKT . ?county rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_city ; geo:hasGeometry ?geomLC . ?geomLC geo:asWKT ?lcnWKT . ?lake rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_stream ; geo:hasGeometry ?geomL . ?geomL geo:asWKT ?lWKT FILTER ( ( geof:sfContains(?oWKT, ?lWKT) && geof:sfContains(?oWKT, ?lcnWKT) ) && strdf:above(?lcnWKT, ?lWKT) ) }

question: Which county in Ireland has the largest park?
sparql: SELECT ?city (strdf:area(?parkWKT) AS ?area) WHERE { ?city rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_County_Council ; geo:hasGeometry ?geoc . ?geoc geo:asWKT ?cWKT . yago:Republic_of_Ireland geo:hasGeometry ?geom . ?geom geo:asWKT ?iWKT FILTER geof:sfContains(?iWKT, ?cWKT) ?park rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_park ; geo:hasGeometry ?parkGeom . ?parkGeom geo:asWKT ?parkWKT FILTER geof:sfContains(?cWKT, ?parkWKT) } ORDER BY DESC(?area) LIMIT 1

question: Which streams intersect Unitary Authority Wards in Edinburgh?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?stream WHERE { yago:Edinburgh geo:hasGeometry ?rep1 . ?rep1 geo:asWKT ?WKT1 . ?UnitaryAuthorityWard rdf:type y2geoo:OS_UnitaryAuthorityWard ; geo:hasGeometry ?rep2 . ?rep2 geo:asWKT ?WKT2 FILTER geof:sfContains(?WKT1, ?WKT2) ?stream rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_stream ; geo:hasGeometry ?rep3 . ?rep3 geo:asWKT ?WKT3 FILTER geof:sfIntersects(?WKT2, ?WKT3) }

question: Which county of England has the largest forest?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?county (strdf:area(?geoWKT) AS ?totalArea) WHERE { yago:England geo:hasGeometry ?egeo . ?egeo geo:asWKT ?eWKT . ?county rdf:type y2geoo:OS_County ; geo:hasGeometry ?geomC . ?geomC geo:asWKT ?cWKT FILTER geof:sfContains(?eWKT, ?cWKT) ?forest rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_forest ; geo:hasGeometry ?o2 . ?o2 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT2 FILTER geof:sfWithin(?geoWKT2, ?cWKT) } ORDER BY DESC(?totalArea) LIMIT 1

question: Which greek municipalities have more than 5 beaches?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?mun (COUNT(?beach) AS ?beaches) WHERE { { SELECT DISTINCT ?mun ?beach WHERE { ?mun rdf:type y2geoo:GAG_Municipality ; geo:hasGeometry ?a . ?a geo:asWKT ?A . ?beach rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_beach ; geo:hasGeometry ?b . ?b geo:asWKT ?B FILTER strdf:contains(?A, ?B) } } } GROUP BY ?mun HAVING ( ?beaches > 5 )

question: In which barony is Coolea located?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?barony WHERE { yago:geoentity_Coolea_3300151 geo:hasGeometry ?o . ?o geo:asWKT ?cooleaGeo . ?barony rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_Barony ; geo:hasGeometry ?o2 . ?o2 geo:asWKT ?baronyGeo FILTER geof:sfWithin(?cooleaGeo, ?baronyGeo) }

question: Are there any forests in a 10km radius from Kastanas beach?
sparql: ASK WHERE { yago:geoentity_Paralía_Kastanás_10277719 geo:hasGeometry ?rep1 . ?rep1 geo:asWKT ?kWKT . ?forest rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_forest ; geo:hasGeometry ?rep2 . ?rep2 geo:asWKT ?fWKT FILTER ( geof:distance(?kWKT, ?fWKT, uom:metre) <= 10000 ) }

question: Is Tripoli closer to Athens than Ioannina?
sparql: ASK WHERE { <http://yago-knowledge.org/resource/Tripoli,_Greece> geo:hasGeometry ?tgeom . ?tgeom geo:asWKT ?twkt . yago:geoentity_Dimos_Athens_8133876 geo:hasGeometry ?ageom . ?ageom geo:asWKT ?awkt . yago:geoentity_Dimos_Ioannina_7303595 geo:hasGeometry ?igeom . ?igeom geo:asWKT ?iwkt FILTER ( geof:distance(?twkt, ?awkt, uom:metre) < geof:distance(?iwkt, ?awkt, uom:metre) ) }

question: Identify any nature reserves that are situated south of a forested area.
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?nature_reserve WHERE { ?nature_reserve rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_nature_reserve ; geo:hasGeometry ?nature_reserve_geo . ?nature_reserve_geo geo:asWKT ?nature_reserve_geoWKT . ?forest rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_forest ; geo:hasGeometry ?forest_geo . ?forest_geo geo:asWKT ?forest_geoWKT FILTER strdf:below(?nature_reserve_geoWKT, ?forest_geoWKT) }

question: Which villages are south of parks in Dublin?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?bay WHERE { yago:Dublin geo:hasGeometry ?geomLC . ?geomLC geo:asWKT ?prkWKT . ?park rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_park ; geo:hasGeometry ?geoPrk . ?geoPrk geo:asWKT ?lWKT . ?bay rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_village ; geo:hasGeometry ?geomL . ?geomL geo:asWKT ?cWKT FILTER ( geof:sfWithin(?lWKT, ?prkWKT) && strdf:below(?cWKT, ?lWKT) ) }

question: Is there a stream located east of a lake in Corfu?
sparql: ASK WHERE { yago:Corfu geo:hasGeometry ?o2 . ?o2 geo:asWKT ?xWKT2 . ?x2 rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_stream ; geo:hasGeometry ?x2Geom . ?x2Geom geo:asWKT ?iWKT2 . ?x1 rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?x1Geom . ?x1Geom geo:asWKT ?iWKT1 FILTER ( ( geof:sfWithin(?iWKT1, ?xWKT2) && geof:sfWithin(?iWKT2, ?xWKT2) ) && strdf:right(?iWKT2, ?iWKT1) ) }

question: Which parks are inside counties of England?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?park WHERE { ?county rdf:type y2geoo:OS_County ; geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?countyGeo . ?park rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_park ; geo:hasGeometry ?o2 . ?o2 geo:asWKT ?parkGeo . yago:England geo:hasGeometry ?o3 . ?o3 geo:asWKT ?englGeo FILTER ( geof:sfWithin(?countyGeo, ?englGeo) && geof:sfWithin(?parkGeo, ?countyGeo) ) }

question: What is the smallest district that borders Greater London?
sparql: SELECT ?district WHERE { yago:Greater_London geo:hasGeometry ?rep1 . ?rep1 geo:asWKT ?WKT1 . ?district rdf:type y2geoo:OS_District ; geo:hasGeometry ?rep2 . ?rep2 geo:asWKT ?WKT2 FILTER geof:sfTouches(?WKT2, ?WKT1) } ORDER BY ASC(strdf:area(?WKT2)) LIMIT 1
